<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="surface-panel overflow-hidden">
  <div class="grid gap-8 p-8 md:p-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">About the platform</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-5xl leading-none text-ink-900 md:text-6xl">Malawi discovery, designed with more care and less friction.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-base leading-8 text-ink-700">
      <p>Malawi Hidden Gems is a tourism storytelling platform for travelers and locals who want a cleaner, more premium way to document the places that make Malawi unforgettable.</p>
      <p>We focus on graceful mobile experiences, resilient offline access, high-quality imagery, and destination discovery that still feels polished on slower networks and smaller devices.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid gap-px bg-black/5 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="bg-white px-8 py-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">Editorial</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl text-ink-900">Human stories first.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">Travel memories, local food, adventure routes, wildlife highlights, and regional insights are all shaped into calm, readable experiences.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white px-8 py-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">Technical</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl text-ink-900">Built for unstable internet.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">The app uses optimized image delivery, offline caching, and progressive enhancement so browsing still feels dependable in remote destinations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white px-8 py-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">Ownership</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl text-ink-900">Anonymous, but protected.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">Contributors can publish without accounts while editor tokens stay in the browser, making post updates simple without opening everything to the public.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
